  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/684/717/cbf4e971-7207-4602-bd76-b44081f9b7df.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Resource Pack-16x-green?style=plastic\" /> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/gamerpotion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/buy me a coffee-support-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/uCPfPBvsRJ\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/870825743788158986?color=blue&amp;style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/GamerPotionDev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/my other-projects-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/get%20a%20server-click%20here-blue?style=plastic\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Summary</span></p>\n<p>Custom crosshair made for use on my <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/darkrpg\">DarkRPG</a> modpack. Now released as a standalone.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Description</span></p>\n<p>This will further improve your vanilla experience by changing the standard vanilla crosshair into a modern design crosshair seen in many other games.</p>\n<p><br />Looking for more crosshairs, fonts or resource packs? check out my other projects <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/GamerPotionDev\">Here</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/658/675/2023-05-09_01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1142\" height=\"442\" />&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/434/158/dec51e74-03ba-4abb-920c-bdc47a4e302a.png\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Gamerpotionplus/videos\"><img src=\"https://media.forge